<p>Left side of a <rs type="material" key="marmor">white marble</rs> upper <rs type="objectType">statue base</rs> plinth comprising a rectangular inscribed area set on a curved element cut in one piece with it (<measure type="length" unit="metre" dim="width">0.55</measure> × <measure type="length" unit="metre" dim="height">0.25</measure> × <measure type="length" unit="metre" dim="depth">0.54</measure>).  The upper surface is treated to receive an upper element.</p>
</div>

